ckages/plugin-workers-core/mod.ts:17-25` re-exports from `src/public/root.ts`, including `inspectTask` and `inspectWorkflow`. `deno doc --filter inspectTask packages/plugin-workers-core/mod.ts` and `deno doc --filter inspectWorkflow packages/plugin-workers-core/mod.ts` both resolve to `packages/plugin-workers-core/src/public/root.ts`.\n4. `plugin-streams-core/src/domain/errors.ts`: no finding. `StreamError` / `StreamSchemaError` have no live repo importers or docs references; current code uses durable-stream client errors in `packages/plugin-streams-core/src/application/create-durable-stream.ts`.\n5. KEEP manifest sample: no wrong-keep findings in four samples. SDK collections remain exported/tested/docs-referenced (`packages/sdk/deno.json:10`, `packages/sdk/tests/type-fixtures/query-collection_type.ts:1`, `docs/site/reference/sdk/index.md:147`); workers bin entrypoints are manifest/Aspire/test/docs-coupled (`plugins/workers/src/public/mod.ts:69`, `plugins/workers/src/aspire/workers-contribution.ts:52`, `plugins/workers/tests/aspire/workers-contribution_test.ts:50`); service health remains template/runtime/doc coupled; Fresh UI `DataGrid` remains root-exported/tested/docs/CSS-coupled (`packages/fresh-ui/mod.ts:26`, `packages/fresh-ui/tests/data-grid.test.tsx:3`, `packages/fresh-ui/src/presentation/data-grid.css:1`).\n\nIndependent verification run:\n\n- `deno run --allow-read --allow-run .llm/tools/run-deno-check.ts --root packages --ext ts,tsx` — PASS, 1,905 files, 16 batches, 0 diagnostics.\n- `cd packages/cli \u0026\u0026 deno task test` — PASS, 306 passed, 0 failed.\n- `cd packages/plugin \u0026\u0026 deno task test` — PASS, 74 passed, 0 failed.\n- `cd packages/plugin-workers-core \u0026\u0026 deno task test` — PASS, 25 passed, 0 failed.\n- `cd packages/plugin-streams-core \u0026\u0026 deno task test` — PASS, 8 passed, 0 failed.\n- `cd packages/telemetry \u0026\u0026 deno task test` — PASS, 12 passed, 0 failed.\n\nCAVEATS\n","created_at":"2026-07-05T23:42:49Z","